data.description:
A once-in-a-lifetime opportunity awaits with the chance to own a piece of skiing history dating back to the 1930s. This unique ski-in ski-out property offers the perfect blend of history and natural beauty, bordering vast public lands. The property includes a spacious and completely renovated historic lodge and guest cabin, along with storage buildings to accommodate all your needs.

The meticulously maintained ski hill presents a challenging playground for skiers and snowboarders, boasting thrilling lines for those who seek an adrenaline rush. While the ski lift may not be currently operational, this doesn’t stop adventurous individuals from accessing the slopes. Whether it's by snowcat or skinning up, the luxury of skiing and snowboarding in your backyard is a rare opportunity that few will ever experience. Ski or Snowboard nearby Discover Ski area in the morning, and come make fresh tracks at whatever time you would like at home. Cross-country ski trails also meander through the landscape, inviting those who prefer a quiet, serene adventure. 

The heart of this remarkable property is the warm and inviting Lodge. This retreat is ideal for hosting family and friends, or even as a potential vacation rental as each level has all the amenities needed for a comfortable stay. The upstairs has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms including a master suite as well as a full kitchen, living room, and laundry room. Walk downstairs into the “Great Room” where you will find a living room and kitchenette along with two bedrooms and two bathrooms, one of which serves as a utility room with washer dryer hookups as well. Cozy up by the fire after a day on the slopes, take in the breathtaking views, or soak in the rustic ambiance. The deck provides stunning views of the ski hill and serves as a wildlife watching vantage point, adding to the experience of this unique property. There is also a dry cabin for additional guests, ensuring ample accommodation space for everyone to enjoy the tranquility and adventure that this property offers.
The two-car attached garage, shop, and barn provide ample storage space for vehicles, equipment, and your toys! There are five bays in total that can be utilized and are rich with history as well.

This property does not have any covenants or restrictions, and could be tastefully subdivided to create multiple parcels adjoining public land. Don't miss the opportunity to create your legacy in this remarkable​​‌​​​​‌​‌​​​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​​​‌‌​​​​ setting.
